short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Makes Bio-Med all the more holy.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension deletes Bio-Med Science academy from the internet and instead replaces it with references to Fire Emblem: Three Houses. What a great time.

Based on Cloud to Butt Plus.
